  <thing id="spUmAciSpi" name="Acid Spittle" description="You belch forth a small viscous glob of potent acid at a nearby target as a ranged touch attack with a splash weapon. The target takes 1d6 points of acid damage +1 point per caster level (+20 maximum) unless a Reflex save is made for half damage.  Anyone within 5 ft. of where the acid glob strikes takes 1 point of acid damage +1 per two caster levels (+10 maximum) unless a Reflex save is made for half damage. If the acid glob is not spit before the spell&apos;s duration expires, it inflicts maximum damage upon the caster internally (no saving throw) unless otherwise protected from acid." compset="Spell" summary="You belch forth a small viscous glob of potent acid at a nearby target as a ranged touch attack with a splash weapon.">
