  <thing id="spUmChaFla" name="Chaos Flame" description="You create a ball of flame, that does 4d4 damage, that attempts to attack a target within range as a ranged touch attack each round. The caster must make a DC 13 Will save each round to select the target; if he fails, then the fire attacks a random target that round. The caster is never targeted by the spell, but his allies may be. The ball of flame instantly travels anywhere within its range each round to strike a target who can make a Reflex save for half damage.\n\nThis spell can be substituted for {i}fireball{/i} as the 2nd-level domain spell of the Fire domain." compset="Spell" summary="You create a ball of flame that attempts to attack a target within range each round">
